text: got chickens want to keep them alive and thriving let's make it happen one buy quality chicks from trusted suppliers healthy chicks mean fewer losses two protect them from extreme cold use good brooders and central heating to keep them cozy three avoid Suffocation keep the temperature even and avoid loud noises four always wash Drinkers and replace water daily clean water is a must five serve water before feeds it keeps chickens calm and prevents stampedes six prevent diseases know the risks get advice and vaccinate seven never use moldy feeds it's dangerous and can make them sick eight keep Predators out secure your pens from dogs cats and snakes nine follow medication and vaccination schedule strictly it's a lifesaver 10 prevent ammonia build up in litter clean dry litter means healthy Birds 11 maintain proper hygiene it stops diseases from entering your farm 12 Supply sufficient feed wellfed birds are healthy Birds follow these tips to reduce poultry mortality and boost your profits happy farming subscribe
